{"tid":1718946,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果區選取消  整個民間區選有無得做？","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:59:06.000Z","uid":41342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da973cf005fd77602b5bd4b618c2a2031842d412","tid":1718946,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:40.000Z","msg":"呢場係一場民意既公投<br />\n做民間區選好處：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">作更好安排</span></span><br />\n參考公投既如結果  可以調整同令大家alert到個告急情況<br />\n尤其係一區多個泛民競選既情況<br />\n有利令票源集中<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">引起關注</span></span><br />\n實體投票  大排長龍<br />\n一定會引起啲人對區選既關注 增加投票率<span style=\"color: violet;\">（有利有弊）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將來推動</span></span><br />\n有民間區選 亦可有民間立選 特選等等<br />\n和理非最啱做既事 又可做到公民教育<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">可行性低</span></span><br />\n時間 人手不足<br />\n未能判斷是否選民  亦無措施確保一人只有一票<br />\n令人懷疑有好多水份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">危險</span></span><br />\n大排長龍  俾人見到實會告非法集結<br />\n所以風險都高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">成效作打飛機用</span></span><br />\n雖然上面講啲用處 但都係理想化既情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如大家討論下？ 日子  11月24日  如取消/延期區選<br />\n就做個民間區選！"},{"pid":"3e4efa105ce2611c8c1a4164a49f47533dbeecb5","tid":1718946,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"無選民資料點搞？"},{"pid":"5a8e3785706aa948b3f6a9fce851514e9e9f5422","tid":1718946,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e4efa105ce2611c8c1a4164a49f47533dbeecb5","tid":1718946,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"無選民資料點搞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"係好大問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree